{"tid":2036864,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我係數碼暴龍專家....以下10個數碼世界冷知識實嚇你一跳","createTime":"2020-05-26T17:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T05:42:36.000Z","uid":353419,"like":18,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a940162fd5ff861fefa5fd461a68a45f86ab44cb","tid":2036864,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 根據官方遊戲劇情, 賢仔有善良紋章, 理論上蟲蟲獸可以超進化, 唔洗同V仔獸合體<br />\n.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FX7HVoF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFX7HVoF.jpg&h=6b54b8b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 根據官方小說既迪路獸所講.....四聖獸同黑暗掌門人實力平手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iE2dhCk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiE2dhCk.jpg&h=67266c83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.根據官方遊戲劇情, 賢仔係成為暴龍改造者之前, 曾經打嬴過千年獸, 換句話講蟲蟲獸一早封左頂, 係02動畫版第一集已能進究極體<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLXs6zB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLXs6zB.gif&h=d8086a62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6qMEXDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6qMEXDA.jpg&h=a4914bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTauAq5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTauAq5.png&h=5f297495&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4. 根據官方小說, 原來惡魔獸同吸血魔獸全部都係小丑皇手下....只係當時黑暗掌門人忙緊封印四聖獸, 所以唔得閒出手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 根據01版最終話, 紋卡只係增幅器, 只要意念更強, 就算無佢都進到完全體....換句話黎講...如果大輔有料既話,V仔獸本來可以單體進化成飛龍V獸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9jCKjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9jCKjp.jpg&h=d1f86c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.  根據官方遊戲劇情, 其實秋山遼<br />\n先係公認最強被揀選細路, 曾經打嬴過太一, 佢係02回憶片段出現過, 其實佢應該幫拖打鳩究極魔獸同埋吸血魔獸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yvcHVso.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyvcHVso.gif&h=25ec2796&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEAZdd7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEAZdd7.gif&h=72cf730c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7. V仔獸既原主人係秋山遼, 當時單體進化到究極V龍獸, 仲嬴埋千年獸, 後來沉睡係山洞到等大輔黎, V仔獸大慨覺得新主人好廢, 自己逼於無奈要變帝皇龍甲獸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWw2a0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWw2a0Z.jpg&h=0aa8dfee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iyZy17x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiyZy17x.gif&h=c27123b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 數碼裝甲係古代科技, 因為古代種數碼暴龍好難進化, 當時就開發出一堆裝甲, 至於呢堆裝甲係咩人發明....有待考究.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/us3oEVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fus3oEVL.jpg&h=9b3edc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkqFG89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkqFG89.jpg&h=88fef667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9.  火龍獸同古代暴龍獸既實力一樣, 相等於人魂+獸魂, 其實雙鬥魂進化有機會變返古代暴龍獸<br />\n<br />\n10.其實打滅世魔獸果陣情況冇想像中咁絕望, 太一當時唔應該食花生, 佢應該搵青龍獸倖多粒珠佢, 之後進化做奧米加獸幫拖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6TjXQP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6TjXQP.jpg&h=70994998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11. 100條頭髮可以整成黑戰鬥暴龍獸, 如果亞基利獸拎哂所有頭髮, 估計整到隻黑奧米加獸, 秒撚埋青龍獸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rROoE4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrROoE4U.jpg&h=a03aabed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12.  官方漫畫版入面, 飛龍V獸完全體已經打嬴奧米加獸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AOAa4o4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAOAa4o4.png&h=b7b16d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkrhKmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkrhKmV.jpg&h=4f80ed0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n13. 大輔,京子,伊織佢地既D-3暴龍機全部都係仿制品, 係加來老伯仿製賢仔果部始祖品, 後者功能多好多,例如封鎖初代暴龍機進化能力,  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGns6AY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGns6AY.jpg&h=eb29e19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aM2Av2N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaM2Av2N.jpg&h=969e88b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"8401d82dfa724605857bb9e03ba64d2429c5db73","tid":2036864,"uid":115041,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:05:34.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，聽日街頭見"},{"pid":"073e9dce38350ae1d435144ebe3d5d5f7ab79b03","tid":2036864,"uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"想知多啲睇呢個數碼暴龍BLOG<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.xuite.net/link790321/digimon/30648566-%E3%80%8E%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%8D%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%86%92%E9%9A%AA%E7%84%A1%E5%8D%B0%E3%80%8F%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AA%E7%89%88%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97%282016%2F03%2F11%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%29\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.xuite.net%2Flink790321%2Fdigimon%2F30648566-%25E3%2580%258E%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%258D%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2586%2592%25E9%259A%25AA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258D%25B0%25E3%2580%258F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%25BE%2597%25282016%252F03%252F11%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%2529&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=932785f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.xuite.net/link790321/digimon/30648566-%E3%80%8E%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%8D%B8%E5%A4%A7%E5%86%92%E9%9A%AA%E7%84%A1%E5%8D%B0%E3%80%8F%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AA%E7%89%88%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97%282016%2F03%2F11%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%29</a>"},{"pid":"fe853b67331b7e1fd4e54f93f16467bae2a8d0f9","tid":2036864,"uid":8511,"like":79,"dislike":2,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTi